languages.text: "Хочу успеть до того, как не начали ставить эти... Печати. Которые про обманщиков! Ну не обманщица я совсем, понимаете? Даже грокса не одурачу".
"I want to get away before they start putting those... those brands on us. For the tricksters! I'm no kind of trickster, can't you see? I couldn't fool a grox."

languages.text: “我想趁他们……在我们身上打下印记之前赶紧逃走。那些是骗子的印记！可我根本不是骗子，您也看得出来吧？我甚至连格洛克斯兽都骗不过。”
languages.original_text: "I want to get away before they start putting those... those brands on us. For the tricksters! I'm no kind of trickster, can't you see? I couldn't fool a grox."

languages.text: 「あの…あの刻印を押される前に逃げたいんだ。あれは詐欺師に押されるもんだろ？私はそんなんじゃない。わかるよね？蜥蜴牛だって騙せやしないよ」
languages.original_text: "I want to get away before they start putting those... those brands on us. For the tricksters! I'm no kind of trickster, can't you see? I couldn't fool a grox."

languages.text: «Quiero irme antes de que empiecen a ponernos esas... esas marcas. ¡Para los impostores, dicen que son! Yo no soy una impostora, ¿se da cuenta? No engañaría ni a un grox».
languages.original_text: "I want to get away before they start putting those... those brands on us. For the tricksters! I'm no kind of trickster, can't you see? I couldn't fool a grox."

traits.locale_text: «Quiero irme antes de que empiecen a ponernos esas... esas marcas. ¡Para los impostores, dicen que son! Yo no soy una impostora, ¿se da cuenta? No engañaría ni a un grox».

languages.text: "Kaçmazsam düzenbazlar gibi damgalamaya başlayacaklar bizi. Düzenbazlık bende ne gezsin efendim? Buna grokslar bile güler."
languages.original_text: "I want to get away before they start putting those... those brands on us. For the tricksters! I'm no kind of trickster, can't you see? I couldn't fool a grox."

traits.locale_text: "Kaçmazsam düzenbazlar gibi damgalamaya başlayacaklar bizi. Düzenbazlık bende ne gezsin efendim? Buna grokslar bile güler."

languages.text: « Je veux m'en aller d'ici avant qu'ils ne commencent à apposer... ces marques sur nous. Elles désignent les mystificateurs ! Vous ne voyez pas que je n'en fais pas partie ? Je n'arriverais même pas à berner un grox. »
languages.original_text: "I want to get away before they start putting those... those brands on us. For the tricksters! I'm no kind of trickster, can't you see? I couldn't fool a grox."

languages.text: "Ich will davonkommen, bevor sie anfangen ... uns zu brandmarken. Wie Betrüger! Ich bin aber keine Betrügerin, seht Ihr das nicht? Ich könnte keinen Grox hinters Licht führen."
